INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS:

    <Place holder for actual install directions>

SERVER SETUP:

    Apache Instructions:
        * Enable mod_rewrite
        * Use the included .htaccess files
	
    nginx Instructions:
        * Use ProxyPass to an internal Apache server handling your site
        or
        * Check out the example configuration file: 
				INSTALL.nginx (requires nginx >= 0.7.27)

    IIS, Lighttpd, and all other web servers:
        * You're on your own.
